platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With 70 million monthly readers, Wattpad forms a communal experience around the love of writing. Offering words to new readers and a platform to writers, Wattpad creates a kinship between authors and their fans that has never been more intimate.
這款 App 帶來對寫作的熱愛為本的社群體驗。為新讀者提供各式文字內容，並為作家提供平台，讓作家與書迷之間建立深厚的連結。
A communal experience around the love of writing. Offering words to new readers and a platform to writers, there’s a strong kinship here between authors and their fans.
這款 App 是喜愛寫作與閱讀者的社群平台，提供作者與讀者交流空間，幫助創作者與粉絲建立深厚連結。
Une expérience collective autour de l’amour de l’écriture. En offrant des mots au public et une plateforme aux écrivaines et écrivains, un lien étroit s’établit entre les littéraires et leurs fans.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Discover a community of writers, and start writing your story.
Join a global community of readers and writers
